{"tid":2377723,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"你裝咗iOS 14.4未？","createTime":"2021-01-24T00:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T13:24:32.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"60199444393578aceb0f49b7dcc8daf23aa23ecb","tid":2377723,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T00:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.iclarified.com/images/news/79415/386971/386971-1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iclarified.com%2Fimages%2Fnews%2F79415%2F386971%2F386971-1280.jpg&h=c80a19c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRC 如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8623436fc25085621c59689bcd2c2af5f71d4537","tid":2377723,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T00:20:53.000Z","msg":"Apple has seeded iOS 14.4 and iPadOS 14.4 release candidates to developers for testing.<br />\n<br />\niOS 14.4 includes improvements and bug fixes for your iPhone.<br />\n<br />\niOS 14.4 includes the following improvements for your iPhone:<br />\n&bull; Smaller QR codes can be recognized by Camera<br />\n&bull; Option to classify Bluetooth device type in Settings for correct identification of headphones for audio notifications<br />\n&bull; Notifications for when the camera on your iPhone is unable to be verified as a new, genuine Apple camera in iPhone 12, iPhone 12 mini, iPhone 12 Pro and iPhone 12 Pro Max<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThis release also fixes the following issues:<br />\n&bull; Image artifacts could appear in HDR photos taken with iPhone 12 Pro<br />\n&bull; Fitness widget may not display updated Activity data<br />\n&bull; Typing may be delayed and word suggestions may not appear in the keyboard<br />\n&bull; The keyboard may not come up in the correct language in Messages<br />\n&bull; Audio stories from the News app in CarPlay may not resume after being paused for spoken directions or Siri<br />\n&bull; Enabling Switch Control in Accessibility may prevent phone calls from being answered from the Lock Screen<br />\n<br />\nFor information on the security content of Apple software updates, please visit this website:<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/kb/HT201222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fkb%2FHT201222&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TanQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=43f2aed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/kb/HT201222</a>"},{"pid":"4dc9f485f8a0a659118b6a5ef9458387adb9a289","tid":2377723,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T00:28:07.000Z","msg":"Check更新未有，你beta嚟？"},{"pid":"da36643b51482e9fce11cecf7eb1d8152d2a8a92","tid":2377723,"uid":197393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4dc9f485f8a0a659118b6a5ef9458387adb9a289","tid":2377723,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T00:28:07.000Z","msg":"Check更新未有，你beta嚟？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T00:32:59.000Z","msg":"RC"},{"pid":"079b6f09f238b23724f7e35a69460d327ddd2f27","tid":2377723,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"早兩日咪出咗"},{"pid":"181ac50c96dcd40916a5b49c28ea8aa89b51c88a","tid":2377723,"uid":293557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T01:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqcWQiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqcWQiN.png&h=6272d989&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03066d659b8ae2466ba6b8e125086fe730a50652","tid":2377723,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"仲未有雙卡時可簡5G<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebe690eb80b9347c777b3f809db79d8d86194bf","tid":2377723,"uid":380218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T02:29